{"TopicId":39663,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Open Source Construction Techniques for Craft Aesthetics","CreatedByName":"GusTurbo","CreatedById":57552,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-07-28T16:11:32Z","PageNum":47,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal-fan","CreatedById":210003,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-11T18:36:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwho knows how to make an arm (i have the expansion)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni want a very movabale\u00A0arm but i use the blue telescopic and hinges and rotation servos to make it so that it could reach anything\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut when i make it its just so weak and usually messes the whole mission\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso any one ideas ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal-fan","CreatedById":210003,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-11T18:36:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow do i make stock glass ?????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-13T07:40:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStock glass doesn\u0027t exist... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sad:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/sad.png\u0022 title=\u0022:sad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Servo","CreatedById":149419,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-22T01:05:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223924578\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613068615\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210003\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal-fan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/11/2021 at 1:36 PM, Kerbal-fan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow do i make stock glass ?????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223925524\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613202039\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dressian Exploder\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/13/2021 at 2:40 AM, The Dressian Exploder said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStock glass doesn\u0027t exist... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sad:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/sad.png\u0022 title=\u0022:sad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlag parts using with\u00A0semi-transparent flag textures. This example is from Commie_Killer76:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225RFpRfg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.53\u0022 height=\u0022567\u0022 width=\u00221003\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5RFpRfg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-22T08:22:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa. I didn\u0027t even know you could have partially transparent flag textures!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrdinaryKerman","CreatedById":208637,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-24T01:40:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223930325\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221613982151\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dressian Exploder\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/22/2021 at 4:22 PM, The Dressian Exploder said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoa. I didn\u0027t even know you could have partially transparent flag textures!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s always been possible\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Davi SDF","CreatedById":197335,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-16T20:04:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello! I see that this thread has been stagnant for a year, wich is quite sad, because it has some great tips!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo, i made a quick and simple post about something i haven\u0027t seen to be talked about here, wich are fairing engines (without mods)!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNOTE: i am using Restock, however, it does not affect the process. You can do the same things i did with a completely stock game.\u003Cbr\u003E\nALSO: Yes, this could be considered cheating, as you can clip many engines in to a small space. But if you want to, you could just add one!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nFirst, you will need a fairing, i chose the simple 1.25 meters fairing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Wa6zyuH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Wa6zyuH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou will need to flip it upside down:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022RZPbTau.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RZPbTau.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen, you start making your combustion chamber:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KgRlTdJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KgRlTdJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Mf7ln0t.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Mf7ln0t.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen you make the throat and the engine bell:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222lpAiil.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2lpAiil.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can change the fairing color so it looks better, i chose a metalic color.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fysGkKg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/fysGkKg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, add your engines of choice! I chose the Mastodon, great engines due to their radial attachment!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dPcjxW0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dPcjxW0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlmost done! Now you have to de-activate the fairing expansion and it\u0027s staging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022IpE1HRg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/IpE1HRg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood, now, if you want to, you can make a Boat-tail using larger fairings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022yn1Wfqk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yn1Wfqk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDe-activate it\u0027s staging too...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022nJTIvzP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nJTIvzP.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd done! (NOTE: this might look better than in stock due to Restock and WaterFall, but i assure you, you can make great engines with this technique!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022M1Q0S86.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/M1Q0S86.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VHW1iAn.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VHW1iAn.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use\u00A0 fairings to make MANY things! Like a huge TurboJet as an example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022go5Snoc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/go5Snoc.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022vsIAWrg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/vsIAWrg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr a low power and efficient engine:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221duHDyl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/1duHDyl.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022hI51BB3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/hI51BB3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOR Sea-Dragon worthy engines!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022V4zTNi2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/V4zTNi2.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FmUmbib.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/FmUmbib.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n; )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nBasically, you can use fairings to make custom looking engines. Imagine all types of engines! Huge! Weird! HUMONGOUS! Nuclear!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nYou can even make dual mode engines by adding two diferent engines onto the same Fairing Engine!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThank you for reading this, i hope you have some ideas for great engines! I wish you all well. Bye!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-03-12T01:04:46Z\u0022 title=\u002203/12/2022 01:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 12, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Davi SDF\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ETypos and formating\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mephisto81","CreatedById":173062,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-20T00:44:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EShenaningans with drag and engine plates!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nFairings and engine plates are both useful for drag shielding.\u003Cbr\u003E\nEngines plates can also support many more nodes than intended!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nFor reasons unknown, engine plates with a shroud do not only shield the attached parts at the back, but also the part at the front.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe can use this, to shield the whole body of a craft from drag:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mC8U0m0.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/mC8U0m0.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a very small and basic lander for JNSQ. The whole body, the engines and the docking port at the back are shielded from drag. Only the engine plate itself produces a small amount of drag.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAs slowing down with a dragless body is impractical, wings and elevons provide lift and drag when needed for reentry and crossrange capabilities.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TPmZXA3.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/TPmZXA3.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xLcpKmA.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xLcpKmA.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EA 1.25m fairing is the basis.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EAn engine plate is added to the fairing. Shrouded engine plates have some unique features: they shield the parts at the back from drag AND they shield the part in front of it from drag as well for reasons unknown. This way, the fairing, the engines and the docking port are shielded from drag.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SFeL4vQ.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SFeL4vQ.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ETo activate the shroud, a part needs to be added at the back. Here, a reaction wheel is added to activate the shroud and the magical shielding properties. In this state, the reaction wheel would still produce significant amount of frontal plate drag. To avoid this, it is later offset inside the fairing to be shielded as well.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cacKfXw.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/cacKfXw.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThere is a trick to add more items to the engine plate: \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003Eafter we have already used the 4\u002B1 nodes (the docking port is offset for a better view), the engine plate can set again to new nodes, where additional parts can be added, all shielded from drag when inside the shroud.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022w8ukrX2.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/w8ukrX2.jpeg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ETime for a check on the runway! All relevant parts are dragless. Only the elevons, the wings and the airbrake now produce drag (and lift).\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ELink to the craft:\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Mephisto/Dolphin-Mk-I-dragless-lander-for-JNSQ\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalx.com/Mephisto/Dolphin-Mk-I-dragless-lander-for-JNSQ\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLink to the imgur album with the whole construction process:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/gallery/KAeSTGX\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/gallery/KAeSTGX\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Mephisto-\u003Cbr\u003E\n(\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\u0022\u003EFlying like a leaf in the wind! Without drag? How?)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-02-20T00:45:58Z\u0022 title=\u002202/20/2022 12:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 20, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Mephisto81\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EFormating.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zacspace","CreatedById":188888,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-21T23:28:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224094032\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645317855\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173062\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mephisto81\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/19/2022 at 7:44 PM, Mephisto81 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFairings and engine plates are both useful for drag shielding.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had no idea that engine plates had any aerodynamic effect at all! In my SSTOs I used structural tubes and fairings to achieve the same result. I could probably both improve them and eliminate the making history dependency with this technique.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astra Infinitum","CreatedById":221662,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T05:37:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224092703\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645041843\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197335\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Davi SDF\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/16/2022 at 2:04 PM, Davi SDF said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello! I see that this thread has been stagnant for a year, wich is quite sad, because it has some great tips!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo, i made a quick and simple post about something i haven\u0027t seen to be talked about here, wich are fairing engines (without mods)!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNOTE: i am using Restock, however, it does not affect the process. You can do the same things i did with a completely stock game.\u003Cbr\u003E\nALSO: Yes, this could be considered cheating, as you can clip many engines in to a small space. But if you want to, you could just add one!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nFirst, you will need a fairing, i chose the simple 1.25 meters fairing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Wa6zyuH.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Wa6zyuH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Wa6zyuH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou will need to flip it upside down:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RZPbTau.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022RZPbTau.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RZPbTau.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen, you start making your combustion chamber:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KgRlTdJ.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KgRlTdJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KgRlTdJ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Mf7ln0t.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Mf7ln0t.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Mf7ln0t.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen you make the throat and the engine bell:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2lpAiil.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222lpAiil.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2lpAiil.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can change the fairing color so it looks better, i chose a metalic color.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/fysGkKg.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022fysGkKg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/fysGkKg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, add your engines of choice! I chose the Mastodon, great engines due to their radial attachment!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dPcjxW0.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dPcjxW0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dPcjxW0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlmost done! Now you have to de-activate the fairing expansion and it\u0027s staging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/IpE1HRg.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022IpE1HRg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/IpE1HRg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood, now, if you want to, you can make a Boat-tail using larger fairings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yn1Wfqk.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022yn1Wfqk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yn1Wfqk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDe-activate it\u0027s staging too...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nJTIvzP.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022nJTIvzP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nJTIvzP.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd done! (NOTE: this might look better than in stock due to Restock and WaterFall, but i assure you, you can make great engines with this technique!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/M1Q0S86.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022M1Q0S86.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/M1Q0S86.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VHW1iAn.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VHW1iAn.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VHW1iAn.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can use\u00A0 fairings to make MANY things! Like a huge TurboJet as an example:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/go5Snoc.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022go5Snoc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/go5Snoc.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/vsIAWrg.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022vsIAWrg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/vsIAWrg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr a low power and efficient engine:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/1duHDyl.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00221duHDyl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/1duHDyl.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/hI51BB3.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022hI51BB3.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/hI51BB3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOR Sea-Dragon worthy engines!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/V4zTNi2.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022V4zTNi2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/V4zTNi2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/FmUmbib.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FmUmbib.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.67\u0022 height=\u0022750\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/FmUmbib.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n; )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nBasically, you can use fairings to make custom looking engines. Imagine all types of engines! Huge! Weird! HUMONGOUS! Nuclear!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nYou can even make dual mode engines by adding two diferent engines onto the same Fairing Engine!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThank you for reading this, i hope you have some ideas for great engines! I wish you all well. Bye!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow do you just stop the fairing construction mid-fairing-build to be able to make things like that? i can never do it. at best i can use a fairing and make it into a 1.5m to 2.5m adapter or similar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrdinaryKerman","CreatedById":208637,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T10:17:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224141135\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221654321074\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221662\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Astra Infinitum\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Astra Infinitum said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow do you just stop the fairing construction mid-fairing-build to be able to make things like that? i can never do it. at best i can use a fairing and make it into a 1.5m to 2.5m adapter or similar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BLeftClick, iirc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Second Hand Rocket Science","CreatedById":218328,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-11T08:28:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyo it\u0027d be nice if all the construction techniques weren\u0027t so old the pages don\u0027t exist anymore innit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Linkageless","CreatedById":201088,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-25T16:13:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDockable RAPIER with Shielded Docking Port\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found that a Shielded Docking Port can be nicely offset into a RAPIER to provide handy rear docking for small spaceplanes. \u00A0 It also (as I recall) provides a useful reduction in drag on the RAPIER, leaving the front of your stack clear for an inline intake or whatever else.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen closed, the engine operates as usual.\u00A0 When open, the docking ring protrudes just a little bit further out of the back, allowing docking as normal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/3TnmeWN\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/3TnmeWN\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00223GfvunV.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/3GfvunV.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always bind an action group to toggle the docking port and disable (not toggle) the engine.\u00A0\u00A0 Throttling up the engine while the port is open is a good method for emergency explosive separation! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... don\u0027t forget some \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u00A0 Docking manoeuvres using this without \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E are possible, but inadvisable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-09-07T20:04:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 1-5 solar panels in a box perfectly fits the cargo bay of the size 2 lander can!\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u0022126.39\u0022 width=\u0022754\u0022 alt=\u0022unknown.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/997580829435895830/1017163051704791050/unknown.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGonna use this in my\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/209636-rutabagas-project-of-the-day/#comment-4172456\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EProject of the day series\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-13T21:45:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224094032\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002239663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645317855\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173062\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mephisto81\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/20/2022 at 1:44 AM, Mephisto81 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly the engine plate itself produces a small amount of drag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOffset the fairing so that the engine plate in \u003Cem\u003Einside\u003C/em\u003E it, I tried it, it works. Completely removes drag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, overheating comes with drag - no drag, no overheat, perfectly safe reentry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}